WEBVTT

00:01.869 --> 00:04.337
Things come up,
you can always call me.

00:04.339 --> 00:06.805
You doing a job
was a one-time thing.

00:06.807 --> 00:09.074
Hey!
You keeping my shit in there?

00:09.076 --> 00:11.276
What's your problem?

00:11.278 --> 00:13.846
Oh, shit.

00:15.350 --> 00:17.083
Craig: Let's do a party
at the Cody place, okay?

00:18.152 --> 00:22.755
Dude, no, no!
It's not that deep, man.

00:22.757 --> 00:25.358
<i> This is the Oceanside</i>
<i> Harbor Patrol.</i>

00:25.360 --> 00:27.927
<i> Stay where you are.</i>

00:29.697 --> 00:31.096
I'm Cassandra.

00:31.098 --> 00:34.099
The devil is just an angel
who lost his way.

00:34.101 --> 00:35.434
-Go wait in the car.
-Dad!

00:35.436 --> 00:37.102
Don't look at her.
Just go. Go!
It's okay, baby.

00:37.104 --> 00:38.704
I just wanted to see him.

00:38.706 --> 00:40.839
He's my son, too!

00:40.841 --> 00:42.575
So why did you even
let him take him?

00:42.577 --> 00:44.043
Let him take him?

00:44.045 --> 00:46.712
I would do anything
to have Henry back.

00:46.714 --> 00:48.181
That you were trying
to set me up!

00:48.183 --> 00:49.982
Wait a minute. I don't know
what you're talking about.

00:49.984 --> 00:51.450
Who showed up?
What's going on?

00:51.452 --> 00:53.919
DEA.
Livingood.

00:53.921 --> 00:54.987
Well, did he find it?

00:54.989 --> 00:57.122
I got rid of it.
What?

00:57.124 --> 00:59.058
I'm not going to federal prison
for your bullshit.

00:59.060 --> 01:01.326
It's not my fault that you have
heat on you right now.

01:01.328 --> 01:05.664
The only thing this guy seemed
to care about was Deran.

01:05.666 --> 01:12.137
♪♪

01:12.139 --> 01:17.876
♪ She stares deeply ♪

01:17.878 --> 01:21.881
♪ Locked inside me ♪

01:21.883 --> 01:27.552
♪ Burnin' brightly ♪

01:27.554 --> 01:33.692
♪ One they know
that I cannot take ♪

01:33.694 --> 01:36.895
♪ Waitin' for it all to begin ♪

01:36.897 --> 01:43.702
♪ Every night now, they'll win ♪

01:43.704 --> 01:46.705
♪ Come and meet my black hole ♪

01:46.707 --> 01:50.576
♪ Got a big black hole ♪

01:50.578 --> 01:54.379
♪ Got a big black hole ♪

01:54.381 --> 01:58.250
♪ I've got a big black hole ♪

01:58.252 --> 02:02.121
♪ I've got a big black,
big black hole ♪

02:02.123 --> 02:06.325
♪ Got a big black hole
inside of me ♪

02:06.327 --> 02:08.527
♪ Got a ♪

02:08.529 --> 02:14.133
♪♪

02:14.135 --> 02:16.601
18-karat white gold.

02:16.603 --> 02:19.038
Box catch clasp
with a hidden safety.

02:22.209 --> 02:24.310
Janine: Ugh.
I want them all.

02:26.281 --> 02:29.882
Now, this one --
53 round-cut stones.

02:32.820 --> 02:35.220
They're beautiful.

02:35.222 --> 02:37.356
But do you have
anything larger?

02:37.358 --> 02:38.223
Of course.

02:38.225 --> 02:41.694
Let me show you these.

02:41.696 --> 02:43.996
Now, I think you'll find --

02:45.566 --> 02:49.234
Uh, e-excuse me.

02:49.236 --> 02:50.303
What are they doing?

02:50.305 --> 02:52.905
I'm not sure.
E-Excuse me.

02:52.907 --> 02:54.373
W-What is going on here?

02:54.375 --> 02:55.574
Termite treatment.

02:55.576 --> 02:57.143
We got a work order.

02:58.980 --> 03:02.247
Can you smell that?
It's horrible.

03:02.249 --> 03:05.584
May I see the work order,
please?

03:05.586 --> 03:06.919
It's in the truck.

03:06.921 --> 03:09.355
Well, I wasn't notified
about any of this.

03:13.060 --> 03:14.927
Um,
perhaps I should leave.

03:14.929 --> 03:16.195
Oh, ma'am, if you'll give me
just a moment.

03:16.197 --> 03:17.596
Uh, I really --
I can't.

03:17.598 --> 03:19.798
It's just too horrible.

03:19.800 --> 03:20.933
This is outrageous.

03:20.935 --> 03:22.467
You're driving
customers away.

03:22.469 --> 03:23.602
Now, I demand to see

03:23.604 --> 03:26.539
some form of identification
immediately.

03:26.541 --> 03:27.806
Don't do anything stupid.

03:27.808 --> 03:29.274
Don't even
think about it.

03:29.276 --> 03:30.475
Back up.
Okay.

03:30.477 --> 03:32.345
Back up. Open the gate.
Alright, alright.

03:32.347 --> 03:33.946
Keys on the counter.

03:33.948 --> 03:35.280
Okay.
On the counter, now.

03:35.282 --> 03:37.950
Okay.
Hands behind your back.

03:37.952 --> 03:39.151
Tell you what,
keep your mouth shut,

03:39.153 --> 03:41.320
this can go really
nice and easy.

03:43.958 --> 03:45.624
Come here.
Sit down.

03:45.626 --> 03:47.360
Get down.
-Okay.

03:47.362 --> 03:55.034
♪♪

03:55.036 --> 04:02.775
♪♪

04:02.777 --> 04:10.449
♪♪

04:10.451 --> 04:12.918
Nobody be a hero.

04:12.920 --> 04:14.987
Alright, let's move!

04:14.989 --> 04:23.863
♪♪

04:23.865 --> 04:32.938
♪♪

04:32.940 --> 04:35.941
[ Alarm ringing ]

04:35.943 --> 04:38.143
♪♪

04:38.145 --> 04:40.545
[ Engine starts ]

04:40.547 --> 04:43.949
♪♪

04:43.951 --> 04:46.285
Next time,
you're the decoy.

04:46.287 --> 04:48.487
That was boring
as hell.

04:48.489 --> 04:52.291
Oh, like anybody's bending over
backwards for my Black ass.

04:52.293 --> 04:53.626
We got to get the watches.
Get the watches!

04:53.628 --> 04:56.962
No, leave the watches.
Just get the bracelets.

04:56.964 --> 04:59.432
Let's go, let's go,
let's go.

04:59.434 --> 05:08.441
♪♪

05:08.443 --> 05:09.842
Let's go!

05:09.844 --> 05:12.978
♪♪

05:12.980 --> 05:14.847
-Drive!
-Ah!

05:14.849 --> 05:16.515
♪♪

05:16.517 --> 05:18.985
[ Horn honking ]

05:31.933 --> 05:40.739
♪♪

05:40.741 --> 05:49.615
♪♪

05:49.617 --> 05:58.423
♪♪

05:58.425 --> 06:07.032
♪♪

06:07.034 --> 06:09.568
[ Water splashing ]

06:09.570 --> 06:18.711
♪♪

06:18.713 --> 06:28.053
♪♪

06:28.055 --> 06:29.855
Jesus --

06:29.857 --> 06:32.057
-Get out.
-Uh -- uh --

06:32.059 --> 06:33.125
Out.

06:33.127 --> 06:34.193
Okay, okay, hold on.
Hold on a second.

06:34.195 --> 06:35.728
Just hold on, alright?

06:35.730 --> 06:37.863
Out!

06:37.865 --> 06:40.866
Keep your hands up!
Okay, okay.

06:40.868 --> 06:42.001
Okay.

06:42.003 --> 06:44.537
Let's go.
Come on.

06:46.607 --> 06:49.542
Hey, you're that lowlife that
was hanging with Cassie, huh?

06:49.544 --> 06:50.876
Shut up.

06:50.878 --> 06:52.411
That what this was?
When you were swimming?

06:52.413 --> 06:54.680
On your knees. Shut up!
Casing the place?

06:54.682 --> 06:55.814
That stupid bitch.

06:55.816 --> 06:57.016
Hands behind your head.

06:57.018 --> 06:58.551
Okay.

06:58.553 --> 07:04.289
♪♪

07:04.291 --> 07:05.358
[ Ties zip ]

07:05.360 --> 07:07.092
Open up.
Open up.

07:07.094 --> 07:09.161
[ Grunting ]

07:09.163 --> 07:21.707
♪♪

07:21.709 --> 07:23.508
Hey.

07:23.510 --> 07:25.178
What?

07:25.180 --> 07:27.446
Get up.

07:27.448 --> 07:30.783
You're the guy
who was with my mom.

07:30.785 --> 07:31.984
Dad? Dad!

07:31.986 --> 07:33.452
Henry, hey.

07:33.454 --> 07:34.720
It's okay, Henry.

07:34.722 --> 07:37.522
It's okay.
He's coming with us.

07:37.524 --> 07:38.857
Just -- Hey!
Henry, Henry, Henry!

07:38.859 --> 07:41.126
Just relax, Henry.
Everything's gonna be okay.

07:41.128 --> 07:44.663
Look at me.
I'm not gonna hurt you.

07:44.665 --> 07:45.530
I promise.

07:45.532 --> 07:46.999
You believe me?
Yes.

07:47.001 --> 07:48.667
Just take whatever you want
and go, alright?

07:48.669 --> 07:50.135
Just please --
Listen.
You listen to me.

07:50.137 --> 07:51.404
I want you to
pack your stuff.

07:51.406 --> 07:54.673
You're not coming back.

07:54.675 --> 07:56.075
Just pack it all up.
We're gonna go.

07:56.077 --> 07:57.476
We're gonna get out of here.

07:57.478 --> 07:59.211
Come on, Henry.
Let's go.

07:59.213 --> 08:09.088
♪♪

08:21.902 --> 08:23.469
Deran.

08:30.044 --> 08:33.246
♪♪

08:33.248 --> 08:35.581
[ Sighs ]

08:35.583 --> 08:41.921
♪♪

08:41.923 --> 08:43.188
Deran, it's J.

08:43.190 --> 08:44.857
Call me.

08:50.798 --> 08:53.866
Such bullshit.

08:53.868 --> 08:55.334
Bike still at Smurf's?

08:55.336 --> 08:56.469
Yeah, I'm gonna
get it later.

08:56.471 --> 08:57.870
Ah, big night, huh?

08:57.872 --> 08:59.138
No, not really.

08:59.140 --> 09:01.340
Could eat, though.
You hungry?

09:01.342 --> 09:02.875
-No.
-I'm starving.

09:02.877 --> 09:04.877
Okay, keep it down.

09:04.879 --> 09:07.212
What's your problem?
Oh, I don't know.

09:07.214 --> 09:08.481
I just spent a grand
on your bail.

09:08.483 --> 09:11.216
How about a "thank you"?

09:11.218 --> 09:12.885
Thank you.
Alright?

09:17.158 --> 09:19.292
I have to get to Tonya's.

09:19.294 --> 09:21.394
Well, as long
as you're taking Nick.

09:25.232 --> 09:27.232
[ Sighs ]
[ Jeep door opens ]

09:27.234 --> 09:29.902
Fine.

09:29.904 --> 09:31.837
[ Sighs ]

09:31.839 --> 09:38.377
♪♪

09:38.379 --> 09:45.250
♪♪

09:45.252 --> 09:51.790
♪♪

09:51.792 --> 09:53.258
What the hell
does he want?

09:53.260 --> 09:54.894
How the hell do I know?

09:57.131 --> 09:59.298
[ Door slams ]

10:02.269 --> 10:03.468
What are you
doing here, man?

10:03.470 --> 10:05.338
We need to talk.

10:05.340 --> 10:06.405
Where's Deran?

10:06.407 --> 10:07.673
How the hell
should I know?

10:07.675 --> 10:10.275
He's not answering
my texts.

10:10.277 --> 10:12.477
What's the problem?

10:12.479 --> 10:13.546
I talked to Pete
last night.

10:13.548 --> 10:15.280
Oh, yeah?
You get us our money?

10:15.282 --> 10:17.883
No.
He gave me this.

10:17.885 --> 10:21.420
An agent showed up
asking questions about Deran.

10:21.422 --> 10:23.322
You know who that is?

10:25.226 --> 10:27.593
Yeah, this was the cop
that busted Adrian.

10:30.297 --> 10:32.298
Thought Deran dealt
with that shit.

10:36.170 --> 10:38.637
Shit.

10:38.639 --> 10:41.374
Alright, where is he?
Adrian.

10:43.510 --> 10:46.511
Indonesia.

10:46.513 --> 10:49.048
Is that why the DEA
is circling Deran right now?

10:49.050 --> 10:51.116
Because if this Livingood guy
knows that

10:51.118 --> 10:52.851
we're working with Pete,
what else does he know?

10:52.853 --> 10:55.654
DEA don't know shit.
Pete ain't gonna say anything.

10:55.656 --> 10:58.857
They're just fishing around,
hoping we'll overreact.

10:58.859 --> 11:01.727
Well, Pete flushed the coke.
What?

11:01.729 --> 11:03.662
Yeah, that's what happens
when the DEA shows up.

11:03.664 --> 11:05.530
What was it doing at Pete's?
Deran told me to move it.

11:05.532 --> 11:07.066
To Pete's?
It doesn't matter, man.

11:07.068 --> 11:08.768
It's gone.

11:10.271 --> 11:11.670
What do you mean
it's gone, bro?

11:11.672 --> 11:13.406
I can't be back
to zero right now.

11:13.408 --> 11:14.740
I know. That's why
we need to find Deran

11:14.742 --> 11:16.208
and we need to
sort this out.
Deran?

11:16.210 --> 11:17.676
This is on you.
Me?

11:17.678 --> 11:19.078
You lied about this job
in the first place...

11:19.080 --> 11:20.746
Me?
...saying that
this was cash.

11:20.748 --> 11:22.582
This shit started with you.

11:25.352 --> 11:27.053
What, you got nothing
to say now?

11:29.424 --> 11:31.957
Adrian was Deran's problem,

11:31.959 --> 11:33.225
but now
he's all of our problem.

11:33.227 --> 11:34.960
Do you understand that?

11:34.962 --> 11:42.167
♪♪

11:42.169 --> 11:49.174
♪♪

11:49.176 --> 11:51.110
Deran! Been a while
since you've been

11:51.112 --> 11:52.511
down here to Trestles.

11:52.513 --> 11:53.646
Hey, man.

11:53.648 --> 11:55.380
Waves at home blown out?

11:55.382 --> 11:56.782
Yeah, something like that.

11:56.784 --> 11:58.851
Good to see you
out in the water, bro.

11:58.853 --> 12:06.859
♪♪

12:06.861 --> 12:14.901
♪♪

12:26.447 --> 12:28.581
[ Cellphone buzzing ]

12:30.918 --> 12:31.917
Hello?

12:31.919 --> 12:34.186
<i> Josh?</i>
<i> It's Lark Johnson.</i>

12:34.188 --> 12:35.721
Hey.

12:35.723 --> 12:37.323
<i> I have an addendum to</i>
<i> the probate documents</i>

12:37.325 --> 12:39.124
<i> I need to get to you</i>
<i> for signatures.</i>

12:39.126 --> 12:40.926
Oh, yeah.
You can FedEx them to the house.

12:40.928 --> 12:43.062
<i> Well, actually, I'm in</i>
<i> San Diego for a conference.</i>

12:43.064 --> 12:46.866
<i> So if there's any chance you</i>
<i> could come by and pick them up?</i>

12:46.868 --> 12:48.267
Uh...

12:48.269 --> 12:51.270
<i> I'd like to keep the paper</i>
<i> trail on this to a minimum.</i>

12:51.272 --> 12:53.673
<i> Obviously.</i>

12:53.675 --> 12:54.940
Yeah.
Uh, yeah, sure.

12:54.942 --> 12:56.542
I'll text you
when I'm close.

12:56.544 --> 12:58.344
I'm gonna be a while.

12:58.346 --> 13:00.780
[ Engine idling ]

13:02.750 --> 13:06.452
[ Engine revs, tires screech ]

13:13.227 --> 13:22.502
♪♪

13:22.504 --> 13:32.177
♪♪

13:32.179 --> 13:41.387
♪♪

13:41.389 --> 13:51.063
♪♪

13:51.065 --> 14:00.339
♪♪

14:00.341 --> 14:01.673
Ah!

14:01.675 --> 14:09.549
♪♪

14:09.551 --> 14:17.556
♪♪

14:17.558 --> 14:25.431
♪♪

14:25.433 --> 14:27.699
[ Engine starts ]

14:27.701 --> 14:37.076
♪♪

14:47.789 --> 14:51.323
How much is that bitch
paying you?

14:51.325 --> 14:55.060
Look, whatever it is,
I'll double it.

14:55.062 --> 14:56.796
Hey, man, why don't you just
take my watch?

14:56.798 --> 14:58.664
You'll get at least
30 grand for it.

14:58.666 --> 15:00.800
She's not paying me.

15:02.670 --> 15:04.804
I'm not gonna hurt you, kid.

15:08.876 --> 15:10.942
You know,
she's a shit mother.

15:10.944 --> 15:14.079
She's not a shit mother.

15:14.081 --> 15:16.948
Whatever you think you know
about Cassie,

15:16.950 --> 15:20.620
whatever she told you,
it's not true -- none of it.

15:26.160 --> 15:28.728
What are we doing?
What are -- Why are we stopping?

15:30.498 --> 15:32.165
Hey, come on.

15:36.838 --> 15:39.571
Hey, why'd we stop?!
Come on!

15:39.573 --> 15:40.906
Henry: Dad!

15:40.908 --> 15:42.041
Give me your feet.

15:42.043 --> 15:43.309
Oh, come on.
Please, no.

15:43.311 --> 15:44.710
-Dad!
-Give me your feet!

15:44.712 --> 15:50.516
♪♪

15:50.518 --> 15:52.918
Come on, man, just...

15:52.920 --> 15:56.588
You -- You don't have
to do this, alright?

15:56.590 --> 15:58.924
Walk.

15:58.926 --> 16:00.326
-Why you doing this?
-Go.

16:00.328 --> 16:01.727
-Dad!
-Why? Come on, please.

16:01.729 --> 16:03.663
-Move, go!
-Okay. Alright, okay.

16:03.665 --> 16:05.130
-Go!
-What are we doing?!

16:05.132 --> 16:08.067
Please, don't!
Don't, don't, don't.

16:08.069 --> 16:09.801
Okay.
Okay, j-j-just wait.

16:09.803 --> 16:11.270
Just wait, just wait.
Just wait, please!

16:11.272 --> 16:13.739
-Go!
-Dad!

16:13.741 --> 16:15.807
Come on, man.
You can't do this. Please.

16:15.809 --> 16:18.143
-Dad!
-Please! My kid, man!

16:18.145 --> 16:20.880
-Dad!
-Down. Now.

16:20.882 --> 16:22.147
[ Crying ]
Please don't do this.

16:22.149 --> 16:24.884
On your knees.
Ah, sh...

16:26.954 --> 16:30.022
Please don't do this.
Please, please!

16:30.024 --> 16:32.491
Dad!
Please don't do this.

16:32.493 --> 16:34.026
Don't do this, please.

16:34.028 --> 16:35.895
My son, man.
Please.

16:35.897 --> 16:37.697
Please don't do this.

16:37.699 --> 16:39.498
Let it happen.

16:39.500 --> 16:41.100
[ Sniffles ]

16:41.102 --> 16:43.369
[ Exhales ]

16:47.775 --> 16:49.775
Just let this happen,
you hear me?

16:52.714 --> 16:54.780
Aah!
[ Groans ]

16:54.782 --> 16:56.181
-Dad!
-[ Groans ]

16:56.183 --> 16:58.450
Henry: Dad!

16:58.452 --> 17:00.386
Why are you doing this?

17:00.388 --> 17:03.723
[ Breathing heavily ]

17:03.725 --> 17:11.797
♪♪

17:11.799 --> 17:20.005
♪♪

17:20.007 --> 17:22.874
Hey, you can't
leave me out here!

17:22.876 --> 17:24.476
Henry!

17:24.478 --> 17:26.946
-Dad!
-Henry!

17:26.948 --> 17:28.547
[ Crying ]
Please!

17:28.549 --> 17:30.816
Aah!
[ Crying ] Dad!

17:30.818 --> 17:33.286
It's okay, Henry!

17:35.623 --> 17:37.823
[ Engine starts ]

17:37.825 --> 17:39.558
Hey!

17:39.560 --> 17:44.964
♪♪

17:44.966 --> 17:48.700
Please!
Henry!

17:48.702 --> 17:53.639
♪♪

17:53.641 --> 17:58.878
♪♪

18:03.918 --> 18:06.652
What, you don't answer
your phone anymore?

18:06.654 --> 18:08.254
I was surfing Trestles.

18:08.256 --> 18:11.056
You drove to Trestles?
There's swells out front.

18:11.058 --> 18:12.959
Well, I like Trestles better.

18:15.597 --> 18:17.296
What's wrong?

18:19.266 --> 18:22.001
Pete flushed the coke.

18:22.003 --> 18:23.803
What?
Yeah, it's gone.

18:23.805 --> 18:26.071
All of it.

18:26.073 --> 18:27.473
Why was it at Pete's?

18:27.475 --> 18:30.943
Because you told J
to take it to Pete's.

18:30.945 --> 18:33.278
No, I told J to take it
to the bowling alley.

18:33.280 --> 18:35.214
Yeah, and he took it
to Pete's.

18:35.216 --> 18:37.016
And then that DEA agent
went around

18:37.018 --> 18:39.418
asking questions about you.

18:39.420 --> 18:42.855
Pete then gets spooked
and then flushes it.

18:45.960 --> 18:47.827
[ Exhales ]

18:47.829 --> 18:49.295
Let me think about this
for a second.

18:49.297 --> 18:51.363
What the hell is there
to think about, man?

18:51.365 --> 18:53.165
Where's J now?

18:53.167 --> 18:55.001
How the hell do I know?

19:00.174 --> 19:01.307
Why are you staring at me
like that?

19:01.309 --> 19:02.774
Because you're the one
that told J

19:02.776 --> 19:04.243
to get rid of the coke
in a flex.

19:04.245 --> 19:05.845
Yeah, 'cause I didn't
want it in the house!

19:05.847 --> 19:09.181
Yeah, because you had the DEA
sniffing around, right?!

19:09.183 --> 19:11.517
We have nothing!

19:11.519 --> 19:13.519
