See you around.

36:31.359 --> 36:33.559
Yeah.

36:33.561 --> 36:35.962
Yeah, you will.

36:35.964 --> 36:37.997
Very soon.

36:40.234 --> 36:42.034
[ Engine starts ]

36:42.036 --> 36:47.373
♪♪

36:47.375 --> 36:52.478
♪♪

36:55.783 --> 36:57.383
You know what?

36:57.385 --> 36:59.518
<i> This</i> is what
we should be doing.

36:59.520 --> 37:00.719
Cash.

37:00.721 --> 37:03.522
Not -- Not -- Not drugs,
not gold, not safes.

37:03.524 --> 37:06.392
You know, I just hit six places
in between here and El Cajon.

37:06.394 --> 37:07.793
Six.

37:07.795 --> 37:09.461
Yeah, so then I can smuggle you
some blow on visitation day.

37:09.463 --> 37:11.531
Oh, yeah?
You talk to Pete?

37:16.136 --> 37:18.004
Get the hell out of my face,
man.

37:18.006 --> 37:19.938
You can't admit
that I'm right?

37:19.940 --> 37:21.407
Just once, huh?
Admit it.

37:21.409 --> 37:23.075
Where the hell
you been, J?

37:23.077 --> 37:24.943
Taking care of some things.
Did you tell him?

37:24.945 --> 37:28.547
You know, I said move the coke,
not move it to Pete's.

37:28.549 --> 37:31.550
You should've told us
about the DEA.

37:31.552 --> 37:33.819
I had it handled.
You lied about the job.

37:33.821 --> 37:37.089
Bullshit.
Did you know about this?

37:37.091 --> 37:38.290
-Shut up, man.
-No, no, no.

37:38.292 --> 37:40.092
-Shut up.
-We're not here because of me.

37:40.094 --> 37:41.694
We're here because
you didn't have the balls

37:41.696 --> 37:43.429
to shoot your boyfriend.

37:43.431 --> 37:51.503
♪♪

37:51.505 --> 37:53.039
Is that what
you think, too?

37:53.041 --> 38:05.183
♪♪

38:05.185 --> 38:07.519
[ Grunting ]

38:07.521 --> 38:09.355
[ Glass shattering ]
Ah!

38:11.325 --> 38:13.159
Son of a bitch.

38:14.528 --> 38:16.662
You like shooting people,
don't you, huh?

38:16.664 --> 38:18.196
You liked watching
Smurf's brains

38:18.198 --> 38:19.531
blow out the side
of her head, huh?!

38:19.533 --> 38:21.067
[ Grunts ]

38:21.069 --> 38:23.936
Smurf said you weren't strong
enough to deal with Adrian.

38:23.938 --> 38:25.471
She was right!

38:25.473 --> 38:33.546
♪♪

38:33.548 --> 38:41.687
♪♪

38:41.689 --> 38:43.289
Enough.

38:46.094 --> 38:49.561
Craig, enough!

38:49.563 --> 38:51.764
Enough!

38:51.766 --> 38:53.966
Craig, get off him.

38:53.968 --> 38:55.901
Craig!

38:55.903 --> 38:57.703
Get off him!

38:57.705 --> 39:00.606
Enough!
Get off him.

39:02.911 --> 39:05.244
[ Gasping ]

39:05.246 --> 39:15.121
♪♪

39:15.123 --> 39:25.063
♪♪

39:25.065 --> 39:26.799
Ah.

39:26.801 --> 39:36.609
♪♪

39:40.548 --> 39:50.222
♪♪

39:50.224 --> 39:59.498
♪♪

39:59.500 --> 40:09.174
♪♪

40:09.176 --> 40:18.650
♪♪

40:18.652 --> 40:28.327
♪♪

40:28.329 --> 40:37.803
♪♪

40:37.805 --> 40:39.471
[ Sighs ]

40:39.473 --> 40:46.412
♪♪

40:46.414 --> 40:53.352
♪♪

40:53.354 --> 41:00.092
♪♪

41:00.094 --> 41:02.195
What the hell happened?

41:05.633 --> 41:08.100
What, today?
[ Exhales ]

41:08.102 --> 41:10.069
Yesterday?
Last week?

41:12.173 --> 41:15.107
You've been gone
a long time, man.

41:15.109 --> 41:16.876
Why is the house trashed?

41:19.046 --> 41:20.813
It's a long story.

41:25.787 --> 41:27.587
Where you been, man?

41:27.589 --> 41:29.322
Doesn't matter.

41:33.595 --> 41:34.726
I'm home.

41:34.728 --> 41:36.528
Yeah?

41:36.530 --> 41:38.464
You get your shit together,
or you gonna act like a psycho

41:38.466 --> 41:40.932
and keep taking off
all the time?

41:40.934 --> 41:50.610
♪♪

41:50.612 --> 42:00.019
♪♪

42:00.021 --> 42:03.022
Craig: Yo, where the hell
have you been?

42:03.024 --> 42:04.624
You guys get into
a fight?

42:04.626 --> 42:06.826
Well, it wasn't really
a fight.

42:06.828 --> 42:11.163
J got his ass kicked.

42:11.165 --> 42:13.132
Looks like he did okay
to me.

42:15.369 --> 42:16.568
Where is he?

42:16.570 --> 42:18.303
Beats me.

42:18.305 --> 42:22.374
♪♪

42:22.376 --> 42:23.509
Ah.

42:23.511 --> 42:26.312
Yeah, man, looks like you
cracked a rib.

42:28.983 --> 42:30.716
[ Inhales sharply ]

42:30.718 --> 42:35.721
♪♪

42:35.723 --> 42:37.589
What?

42:37.591 --> 42:39.158
Yeah, that's crooked.

42:43.665 --> 42:45.298
Alright.
Do it.

42:47.001 --> 42:49.935
Alright.
[ Clears throat ]

42:49.937 --> 42:51.270
You ready?

42:51.272 --> 42:53.472
Yeah.
Alright, on three.

42:53.474 --> 42:55.274
One --
Aah!

42:55.276 --> 42:57.109
Gah!

43:00.081 --> 43:01.681
Yeah, still hideous.

43:01.683 --> 43:05.751
♪♪

43:05.753 --> 43:08.054
[ Grunts ]

43:11.559 --> 43:12.892
Alright.

43:12.894 --> 43:20.499
♪♪

43:20.501 --> 43:27.707
♪♪

43:27.709 --> 43:30.576
Pope:
What's that for?

43:30.578 --> 43:32.712
You going somewhere?

43:32.714 --> 43:34.447
I'm leaving.

43:37.785 --> 43:39.318
No, you're not.

43:41.455 --> 43:43.989
Put it back.

43:43.991 --> 43:45.657
I said put it back.

43:45.659 --> 43:47.326
Put it back!

43:51.532 --> 43:53.865
I'm leaving, Pope.

43:53.867 --> 43:55.601
You leave,
and I'll find you.

43:55.603 --> 44:06.078
♪♪

44:06.080 --> 44:08.280
You should clean that up.

44:08.282 --> 44:10.682
Maybe put some ice on it.

44:10.684 --> 44:15.955
♪♪

44:15.957 --> 44:21.227
♪♪

44:21.229 --> 44:25.164
[ Television playing
indistinctly ]

44:25.166 --> 44:27.032
Come here, little man.

44:27.034 --> 44:28.634
Come here.

44:33.240 --> 44:36.108
Hey, you, wake up.
Come here.

44:36.110 --> 44:37.777
What's wrong?
Nothing.

44:37.779 --> 44:39.478
Just want you
to be with me.

44:41.915 --> 44:45.651
Hey, you're never gonna
leave me, right, baby?

44:45.653 --> 44:48.588
Mm.
Both of you.

44:48.590 --> 44:50.389
You.

44:50.391 --> 44:52.792
You're never gonna
leave me.

44:52.794 --> 44:58.397
♪♪

44:58.399 --> 45:03.803
♪♪

45:03.805 --> 45:06.105
[<i> Screams</i> ]

45:07.875 --> 45:11.010
Good, good, good, good.

45:11.012 --> 45:12.478
That's my babies.

45:12.480 --> 45:20.253
♪♪

45:22.023 --> 45:31.831
♪♪

45:31.833 --> 45:41.373
♪♪

45:41.375 --> 45:43.209
